title: St George Bank's online banking services down
text:
St George customers have been unable to access their online account for 24 hours. Peter Morris Thousands of St George Bank customers have been unable to use online, mobile and telephone banking services for 24 hours.
The system failure has come during a long weekend in NSW, Queensland, South Australia and the ACT, with bank branches closed this Labour Day Monday.
St George says customers can still get funds through ATM and EFTPOS services as well as their credit card.
